summary: Okay so it’s established in Far From Home that Mysterio is from a different universe so does that mean that there is someone who...
body:
Okay so it’s established in Far From Home that Mysterio is from a different universe so does that mean that there is someone who looks like him in Peter’s universe?

What i’m saying is does the person Jake Gyllenhaal exist in the Marvel universe and does someone acknowledge it
